# .vercelignore is the ONLY upload gate for CLI deploys — the Vercel CLI does
# NOT read .gitignore (millerbyte's hard-won gotcha). This repo's working tree
# holds .loot/ (the identity's PRIVATE KEY + keyring) and docs/pitch/ (sealed
# content, loot-only host) — neither may ever reach the builder. Allowlist:
# upload site/ only.
/*
!/site
site/node_modules
site/dist
site/.output
site/.tanstack
site/.nitro
site/.vercel
.env*
